Lustre Build: &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_5/40/&quot;&gt;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_5/40/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Distro/Arch: RHEL6.5/x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
MDSCOUNT=4&lt;br/&gt;
</environment>
